{"tid":278112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉暴動罪港女棄保赴台 台灣移民署證無出境紀錄","createTime":"2017-06-10T07:42:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T08:08:43.000Z","uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"958f382cbe1065f0cc9573823e63593d9c4dca61","tid":278112,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T07:42:20.000Z","msg":"涉暴動罪港女棄保赴台 台灣移民署證無出境紀錄<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本報周四獨家報道，引述消息指， 涉去年旺角騷亂被控暴動罪的18歲少女李倩怡，早前棄保並往台灣欲尋求政治庇護。<br />\n<br />\n今日有指台灣內政部移民署證實，李在今年1月6日入境台灣，按規定應在30日內出境，但目前仍未有離境紀錄，入台證已逾期4個多月。另，台灣的行政院大陸委員會則稱，目前並無收到相關庇護申請個案，強調對於港澳居民申請赴台，均設有相關規定，若有港人逾期停留，當局查獲後將依法處理。<br />\n<br />\n李倩怡所涉案件，原定於今年1月中提訊，但因缺席聆訊而遭法庭發出通緝令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B6%89%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3%E6%A3%84%E4%BF%9D%E8%B5%B4%E5%8F%B0-%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E7%BD%B2%E8%AD%89%E7%84%A1%E5%87%BA%E5%A2%83%E7%B4%80-81896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%25A3%2584%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E8%25AD%2589%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25A2%2583%25E7%25B4%2580-81896&d=vCgATC7UJM1bjoNEo%2FwUYPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=f304323d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B6%89%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3%E6%A3%84%E4%BF%9D%E8%B5%B4%E5%8F%B0-%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E7%BD%B2%E8%AD%89%E7%84%A1%E5%87%BA%E5%A2%83%E7%B4%80-81896</a>"},{"pid":"ae968d767dc53bfdc7997363f44dd470bc34e3e7","tid":278112,"uid":10680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T07:43:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05281410ece5341293e851614fe691653b285327","tid":278112,"uid":47492,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T